{"tid":2499200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子疑冒警致電要求落口供　7人受騙","createTime":"2021-04-21T16:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T05:16:33.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3aab14b49823441e25488d16fd56609cedfe70b9","tid":2499200,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"一名男子懷疑冒警致電市民要求落口供，7人受騙。警方指，今日接獲7名市民查詢，都指收到一名陌生男子來電，對方自稱為駐守警察總部的警員，並提供警員編號，指控事主涉及刑事案件，要求他們前往灣仔警署錄取口供。由於男子能提供事主姓名、出生日期及住址等資料，部分事主信以爲真，前往或致電灣仔警署，發現受騙。 <br />\n<br />\n警方指，並無警務人員相約過事主錄取口供，相信騙徒提供的警員編號為虛構，將案件列作「求警協助」調查。"},{"pid":"affd378bf47633e329cf4b43f2ba1ce69a7635dd","tid":2499200,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"點分?"},{"pid":"de30ef45397a9f415255e9d749a91fbbefb966a5","tid":2499200,"uid":224533,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"affd378bf47633e329cf4b43f2ba1ce69a7635dd","tid":2499200,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"點分?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"竟然畀警員編號，肯定係冒警<br />\n真嘅一定唔會畀"},{"pid":"af162553ce13671266736a220df3a7dd54cbadb0","tid":2499200,"uid":55747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T20:07:14.000Z","msg":"目的係咩？惡作劇？"},{"pid":"04b62595cb6d45137a62b64c5a31562e7783f289","tid":2499200,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af162553ce13671266736a220df3a7dd54cbadb0","tid":2499200,"uid":55747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T20:07:14.000Z","msg":"目的係咩？惡作劇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T20:49:43.000Z","msg":"打俾以前暗戀既女同學拎住址"},{"pid":"9f982c771f59749f416338602b2fec3498783187","tid":2499200,"uid":129361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04b62595cb6d45137a62b64c5a31562e7783f289","tid":2499200,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af162553ce13671266736a220df3a7dd54cbadb0","tid":2499200,"uid":55747,"like":0,"dislik